<td width="40%" style="text-align: center;" rowspan="1"><b><a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Iraq" title="Prime Minister of Iraq">Prime Minister of Iraq</a></b><br />
16 July 1979 – 23 March 1991</td>
<td width="30%" align="center" rowspan="1">Succeeded&#160;by<br />
<b><a href="/wiki/Sa%27dun_Hammadi" title="Sa'dun Hammadi">Sa'dun Hammadi</a></b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="40%" style="text-align: center;" rowspan="1"><b><a href="/wiki/President_of_Iraq" title="President of Iraq">President of Iraq</a></b><br />
16 July 1979 – 9 April 2003</td>
<td width="30%" align="center" rowspan="2"><b>Suspended</b>
<div style="font-size:90%"><a href="/wiki/2003_Invasion_of_Iraq" title="2003 Invasion of Iraq" class="mw-redirect">2003 Invasion of Iraq</a><br />
Offices abolished and power transferred to <a href="/wiki/Coalition_Provisional_Authority" title="Coalition Provisional Authority">CPA</a> and <a href="/wiki/Iraqi_Governing_Council" title="Iraqi Governing Council">IGC</a><br />
Positions re-created in mid-2004</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="text-align:center;">
<td width="30%" align="center" rowspan="1">Preceded&#160;by<br />
<b><a href="/wiki/Ahmad_Husayn_Khudayir_as-Samarrai" title="Ahmad Husayn Khudayir as-Samarrai">Ahmad Husayn Khudayir as-Samarrai</a></b></td>
<td width="40%" style="text-align: center;" rowspan="1"><b><a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Iraq" title="Prime Minister of Iraq">Prime Minister of Iraq</a></b><br />
29 May 1994 – 9 April 2003</td>
</tr>
